	<http://lawd.info/ontology/hasName> "The name of the original donor has been erased throughout Texts II and III and replaced with Gabra ʾAragāwi (e.g., , 21v, 127ra, 128, 132vb, 145ra; see also Additio 1). Several other names were added later into supplication formulas of Texts II and III: his father Mazgaba Śǝllāse (e.g., , 128ra, 130vb, 141va; see also Additio 1), Walatta Krǝstos (e.g., , 153ra; s. also Additio 1), ʿAmda Mikāʾel (e.g., , 137ra, 142ra), Gabra Māryām (e.g., , 142ra), Tasfā Mikāʾel (e.g., , 141ra), Tasfā Ṣǝyon (e.g., , 142ra), Walatta Māryām ( ), ʾAmata Māryām ( ), Walatta Kidān ( )." .
